review: Very polite, explained about the procedures in depth  and excellent treatment provided to my daughter... Best clinical solution right from x-ray availed ...Thanks to Dr.  ... finally about the Clinic... situated in Good ambiance with very good interiors

Mr. Jebin Paul Nesaline is a warm and friendly dentist. It has been 2 weeks since I had my wisdom tooth removed and he has been constantly in touch with me while I recover. Last Monday (about a week after the surgery), he'd asked me to pay him a visit just to check how the healing has been. 

I'd recommend Mr. Jebin to anyone who likes a touch of care and humaneness in a doctor. 

-Karthikeyan Balakumar
Doctor understands our concerns well and gives apt treatment. My daughter tooth treatments going well now.

Great work done by the entire team. Got my smile back.

Would recommend this clinic for expert treatment.
